Juan Filipe created the

00:08:59.050 --> 00:09:04.250
"Laureate Lab-Visual Wordist
Studio", and innovative space

00:09:04.250 --> 00:09:09.790
in the library of California State
University in Fresno; his hometown.

00:09:09.790 --> 00:09:13.120
Here, Juan Filipe mixed
poetry, song,

00:09:13.120 --> 00:09:18.470
and art in wonderfully dynamic
programs for his local community.

00:09:18.470 --> 00:09:21.370
That's for one Filipe
dreamed up today's celebration

00:09:21.370 --> 00:09:28.180
which he has named "Speak the
People/the Spark/el Poema."

